There was one other sighting in Greeneville on or around October 28th 2011
divs: Sighting DetailsThis photo was shot from my back porch, that's how close I am to Greene Mountain here in Greeneville, TN. There was a storm coming and I noticed an unusal amount of clounds rolling down over the mountain so I shot several photos of it. I did not physically see the object when I shot the photo(s),(I shot at least 20 photos, one right after the other and this object only appeared in this one shot), only after I uploaded it to my computer.
Summary: I did not actually see the object, I noticed it after I uploaded my photos. I've seen many orbs, and other objects though since and I have photos of them as well.
